<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #006837;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777777;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #006837;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .code-container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dddddd;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 10px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .verification-code {
        font-size: 24px;
        letter-spacing: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333333;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>ACPN Ota Zone</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <h2>Verify Your Email</h2>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with ACPN Ota Zone. Please verify your
          email address to complete your registration.</p>

        <p>Click the button below to verify your email:</p>
        <a href='{{verificationUrl}}' class='button'>Verify Email</a>

        <p>Alternatively, you can use this 6-digit verification code:</p>
        <div class='code-container'>
          <div class='verification-code'>{{verificationCode}}</div>
        </div>

        <p>This code will expire in 24 hours.</p>

        <p>If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>

        <p>Thank you,<br />ACPN Ota Zone Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>&copy;
          {{year}}
          Association of Community Pharmacists of Nigeria, Ota Zone. All rights
          reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>